data.description: This well-appointed duplex presents two distinct units, each comprising 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Recent updates include full hardy plank on the backside, new sewer pumps on both sides, and various interior enhancements! Unit 14516 Waddesdon features upgraded bathroom tiles and a new oven/stove, while 14514 Waddesdon boasts a new fridge and dishwasher. Fridge conveys, has new cabinets, upgraded light fixtures and both units are fully rented out. Ideal for investors seeking rental income or homeowners exploring rental opportunities!
